name: clustering-nonhierarchi-rshiny
description: The RShiny clustering app enables users to upload data, select k-means or k-medoids algorithms, and perform clustering analysis. It generates interactive plots, clustered data, and supports customization. Users can export results for further analysis, making it ideal for data exploration and pattern recognition.
